name: Rag Quilt Baby Burp Cloth black and pink polka dots
description:
Beautiful hand made rag quilt baby burp cloth.

	Measures 15×12 inches. It has a center layer of soft flannel for extra absorbency. The back is of white flannel.

	Please note: This burp cloth is washed once to start the ragging process on it.

options.name: color pink and black polka dots

name: Satin and lace baby bonnet newborn - 3 months
description:
Ssatin and Lace baby bonnet

	Newborn to 3 month size. Lace edge on top of brim. Also machine embroidery across brim to hold it in place, satin ties. Completely lined for baby’s comfort. So cute!

	Great for reborn dolls too.

name: Baby booties gender neutral Winnie the Pooh
description:
Cute booties for newborns for boys or girls.

	Winnie the Pooh is centered on the front of each bootie. Eeyore is on the bottoms.

	Watch for more of my baby booties soon.

name: Starry Blue flannel burp cloth
description:
Starry Blue flannel burp cloth

	Measure about 18×10 inches. A blue flannel with white stars on one side and white flannel on the other. A new mother can never have too many of these!

	And when baby no longer needs it as a burp cloth it makes a fine snuggle blankie.

name: TOOTH FAIRY PILLOW heart shaped for little girls
description:
Tooth Fair Pillow heart shaped – your little princess will love this!

	It has a pocket on the front to slip her tooth in. Then the pillow goes under her pillow and in the morning, the tooth will have been replaced by money in the little pocket.

	Tooth fairy pillow also has a hanging loop of ribbon (not shown) so when the pillow is not in use it can hang from a dress handle, door knob or bed post.

	Measures about 6 inches across. Features a raw edge ruffle with machine embroidery, pretty bow just above the pocket and hanging loop.
